                                    Default: Mapping
        --targetBED                 Target BED file for targeted or whole exome sequencing
        --tools                     Specify tools to use for variant calling
                                    Available: ASCAT, ControlFREEC, FreeBayes, HaplotypeCaller
                                    Manta, mpileup, MuTect2, Strelka
